# ARIA AI Integration Rules

## Gemini Integration
- Use Google Gemini 2.0 Flash model
- Max 200 output tokens for cost control
- Stream responses for better UX

## Function Calling
- Define tools for property search, document generation, status checks
- Handle tool responses appropriately
- Provide fallbacks for failures

## Context Management
- Always include current screen context
- Pass user role and permissions
- Include recent conversation history
- Limit context to 1000 tokens
